    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions as <i>mental barrier <i>II</i>I</i>, but if you are struck by a critical hit or sneak attack, there is a 25% chance that the additional damage is negated (as <i>light</i> fortification). This does not stack with similar effects that negate the additional damage from a critical hit or sneak attack. In addition, you are immune to <i>mind thrust I</i> and <i>II</i>, and you take half damage from <i>mind thrust I</i><i>II</i>, <i>I<i>V</i></i>, and <i>V</i> (reduced to one-quarter on a successful Will save). This spell can be undercast.</p>",
